reviewText:
the movie worked and came in a good shape!
i recommend it to research labs how need it ..
good luck
If you are planning a trip to Denali, this is a must-have.  It also serves as a great souvenir of your trip.

To Whom It May Concern:

This DVD was not as substantial as others I have viewed.  'Twas of good photographic quality; however, unlike many of the documentaries I have purchased, too many people were part of the DVD instead of more Denali National Park -- its panoply of flora and of fauna, and of its mystifyingly beautiful land.
